author: patrickl
msg: This is a patch to take care of a UI glitch. When Root-node is selected,
the content frame should also get updated to the blank welcome page.
Also, removed check if connector is of type warp (we did not support it
earlier since warp connectors don't conform to the standard
Engine/Host/Context hierarchy). Removed this check since warp connectors
are no longer visible through mBeans.

author: craigmcc
msg: At startup time, create the MBeans for the user database, users, and groups.
This is now ready for building the admin screens.
